<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="community">
    We're a community of
    <span class="break hidden-xs"></span>
    I.T. Professionals
  </h1>

  <div class="container">
    <a id="next-event"></a>
    <p class="lead">Our Next Event</p>
    <h1><%= @current_event.title %></h1>
    <h4><%= friendly_date(@current_event) %></h4>
    <a href="<%= @current_event.url %>" class="btn btn-large btn-danger">
      <i class="fa fa-ticket"></i>
      &nbsp; RSVP to this Event
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-us">
  <a id="about-us"></a>
  <section>
    <header>
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <hr />
    </header>
    <div class="multi-column">
      <p>The Saint John Developer User Group is a community of developers, designers, and managers interested in enhancing the professional
      and technical culture of the I.T. sector in the Saint John region.  We typically organize a meet up on the last Thursday of every
      month at the Big Tide Brewing Company to have a drink, socialize, and hear about community events or take in a presentation.</p>
      <p>If you are interesting in presenting a topic, making announcements, or becoming a sponsors, then please contact us. Our goal is
      to gather the best and brightest members of the community in order to learn from each other.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <p class="centered">
          <a href="https://twitter.com/SJDevUG" class="btn btn-large btn-twitter">
            <i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>
            &nbsp; Follow us on Twitter
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <p class="centered">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/sjdevug" class="btn btn-large btn-facebook">
            <i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
            &nbsp; Join us on Facebook
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <p class="centered">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-large btn-success">
            <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
            &nbsp; Subscribe to our Mailing List
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="container upcoming-events">
  <a id="upcoming-events"></a>
  <section>
    <header>
      <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
      <hr />
    </header>
    <div class="row">
      <% @events.each do |event| %>
        <div class="col-md-<%= column_size %> event">
          <h4><%= event.title %></h4>
          <p class="date"><%= friendly_date(event) %></p>
          <p class="description"><%= event.description %></p>
          <p class="presenter"><%= event.presented_by %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="sponsors">
  <a id="sponsors"></a>
  <section class="container">
    <header>
      <h2>Sponsors</h2>
      <hr />
    </header>
    <p>
      <img src="/assets/sponsors/t4g.jpg"/>
      <img src="/assets/sponsors/enterprisesj.jpg"/>
      <img src="/assets/sponsors/rapidmind.gif"/>
      <img src="/assets/sponsors/swiftradius.png"/>
      <img src="/assets/sponsors/ambir.png"/>
    </p>
  </section>
</div>
